Class ModConnection.State

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum
      • com.motorola.mod.ModConnection.State
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable
    Enclosing class:
    ModConnection

    public static final class ModConnection.State
extends Enum
    This class represents the state of the greybus connection corresponding to a particular protocol. An application should only use this class if it needs to determine the status of a protocol which did not enumerate.
